ChangesetIdMismatch.message:
diff contains elements with changeset IDs %s
which don't match the changeset ID %s that the diff was uploaded to

DeleteMultiple.message: Only one element can be deleted per request.

ForkedChangeset.message: Changeset %s has multiple forks, you must specify a version

IdMismatch.message:
Id mismatch between url parameter and xml.
%s !== %s

InUse.message: Cannot delete an element that is in use

MissingChangeset.message:
Changeset %s not found.
 The element must reference an existing changeset.

MissingChangesetId.message: Missing changeset ID: the element must have a changeset attribute with the id of an open changset

MissingParameter.message:
Missing parameter '%s'.
The parameter has to be the same in the URL (e.g. /api/0.6/nodes?nodes=123,456,789)

PlaceholderIdError.message: Placeholder id is missing or non-unique

TypeMismatch.message: Type mismatch between url parameter and xml.
